Usage: glod-classify [OPTIONS...] [FILE]...

Obtain some basic stats about the characters in FILE.

  -h, --help      Print help and exit
  -V, --version   Print version and exit
      --linewise  Instead of given a total view on the file, return stats for
                    each line.
      --graph     Return an ASCII graph of the character distribution.
      --candle    Return an OHLCV candle.
